Store Returns - Do You Know?
Store returns are FREE and you will get your refund sooner. All you have to do is take your item to your nearest store and hand it over to a member of staff. For opening times please visit www.next.co.uk/stores.
Returning from Home
To use our collection service, place all items into a single parcel and attach one returns label. We will send a courier to collect your items, this service costs £2.50. Enter your details below to arrange a courier collection.
Courier returns are no longer included with nextunlimited for new and renewing customers. Please refer to our nextunlimited FAQs, to check your eligibility for free courier returns, based on your subscription start date.
Just a reminder perishable items such as food, plants, drinks and fresh flowers cannot be returned. This does not affect your right to return faulty items.

Cookie Preference Center

Cookies are used to store or retrieve information from your browser (such as Chrome) or device (computer or phone). This information may be about you, your preferences, your device or your settings and is used to allow our website to work and ensure the security of our site. It also helps add functionality and improve your experience, offering a personalised experience and ensuring ads are relevant to you. You can exercise your rights over some categories of cookies below. You may also be able to block the use of Cookies through your browser. For more information, please see our Privacy & Cookie Policy.
